Requirements:
 
* libxml, version 2.3.1 or later (http://xmlsoft.org/, ftp://xmlsoft.org)
* libdb2, the Berkeley database library, it comes with many recent
  Linux distributions.
* You need the XOSD library if you want to enjoy the cool on-screen
  display, this is optional. It can be downloaded from
  http://www.ignavus.net/software.html

For more info, please consult the manpage.
